The '''Dewback Inn''' was a small [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]] located near the [[Galactic Museum/Legends|Galactic Museum]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. Located in the [[Zi-Kree Sector]] of the [[Crimson Corridor]], it was rather disreputable. [[Neimoidian/Legends|Neimoidians]] frequented it because it was one of the few places on Coruscant that served [[Agaric ale/Legends|agaric ale]]. It did not allow [[Droid/Legends|droids]]. It was from this [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]] that [[Darth Maul/Legends|Darth Maul]] tracked [[Hath Monchar]], a Neimoidian who betrayed [[Palpatine/Legends|Darth Sidious]] prior to the blockade over [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]]. Monchar had arranged, at the inn, to sell information about the blockade to [[Lorn Pavan]].

